            . I am shopman to a pawnbroker, in Tothill-street. I have a pair of trousers, pawned by the prisoner on the first of June.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. On leaving my work, I went home, and these trousers were in the window - I thought I might get 1s. for them, and replace them in the morning; I did not know whose they were.</p>
